{% extends 'layout.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Your Personal Learning Plan{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

<h2>Register with Mind Tools</h2>

<p>
    <img class="pull-right" alt="Registration" src="/images/registration.jpg" />
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras venenatis vehicula est,
    ac fermentum mauris tincidunt vel. Fusce dignissim, augue a placerat imperdiet, velit
